sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Controller<br/>(Shelly Pro 4PM)
    participant P as Pump<br/>(Wilo Z20/4)
    participant VI as VI-coll<br/>(on/off)
    participant VO as VO-tank<br/>(on/off)
    participant VA as V_air<br/>(on/off)
    participant FS as Flow Sensor

    Note over C: T_outdoor < 2°C detected
    C->>P: Stop pump
    P-->>C: Pump OFF confirmed

    Note over C: Close all valves first
    C->>VI: Close (if open)
    C->>VO: Close (if open)

    Note over C: Set drain valve states
    C->>VA: Open V_air (air intake)
    C->>VI: Open VI-coll (from collector bottom)
    C->>VO: Open VO-tank (to tank return)
    VA-->>C: Open confirmed
    VI-->>C: Open confirmed
    VO-->>C: Open confirmed

    Note over C: All drain valves set
    C->>P: Start pump

    loop Monitor flow sensor
        FS-->>C: Flow detected (water)
        Note over P: Pumping water from<br/>collectors to tank.<br/>Air entering from top.
    end

    FS-->>C: Flow = 0 (collectors empty)
    C->>P: Stop pump
    C->>VA: Close V_air
    C->>VI: Close VI-coll
    C->>VO: Close VO-tank
    Note over C: Drain complete.<br/>Collectors empty and safe.
